	<item>
		<title>Another #madewithcorona hit from Sphere Game Studios: Merge City</title>
		<link>/blog/2019/01/11/another-madewithcorona-hit-from-sphere-game-studios-merge-city/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 11 Jan 2019 20:15:31 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Rob Miracle]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Featured App]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">/?p=76221</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Sphere Game Studios has recently released Merge City and Google Play took notice. Learn more about this fun #madwithcorona game]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href=https://www.spheregamestudios.com/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sphere Game Studios</a> has another hit on their hands with their new title: <em><a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.spheregamestudios.mergecity rel="noopener" target="_blank">Merge City</a></em> which is currently on <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/editorial_collection/promotion_topic_b000054_games_indie_corner_tp target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play&#8217;s &#8220;Indie Corner&#8221;</a> in the &#8220;Our Indie Picks&#8221; section.</p>
<div class="video-responsive"><iframe width="auto" height="auto" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OZtVZ0e83S8?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
<p><em>Merge City</em> is a blend of city building and merge gaming, similar to the game <em>Merge Planes</em>. The game play is simple: You merge two level 1 buildings to unlock a level 2 building. There are 30 different buildings to unlock in two neon-inspired worlds. You can visit other players from the leaderboard and compare your cities to theirs.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-76222" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/merge1-1024x546.png" alt="" width="1024" height="546" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/merge1-1024x546.png 1024w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/merge1-300x160.png 300w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/merge1-768x409.png 768w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/merge1-700x373.png 700w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/merge1-125x67.png 125w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>Merge City is free to play with in-app purchases and is available on both the <a href=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/merge-city/id1444695443 target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple App Store</a> and <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.spheregamestudios.mergecity target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a>. Check it out!</p>
<p><a href=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/merge-city/id1444695443 target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-72086" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a> <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.spheregamestudios.mergecity target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-72174" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
			</item>
		<item>
		<title>#madewithcorona: Mission Me!</title>
		<link>/blog/2018/10/29/madewithcorona-mission-me/</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 29 Oct 2018 16:49:54 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Rob Miracle]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Featured App]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">/?p=76054</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<em>Mission Me</em> is a unique game made with Corona that is worth your time to check out. Learn more about this game!]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Periodically a game comes along that breaks out and does something different. Corona Labs would like to introduce you to <a href=https://missionmeapp.com/ target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Mission Me</em> by Sillysoft Games</a>. <em>Mission Me</em> is a lifestyle game.</p>
<p>In this game, you get missions that you frequently have to do in real life and may require you to get off of your device for a while to accomplish. As you complete missions, you gain experience and move up to more missions. Example missions include things like &#8220;Clean up your desk and add a decoration&#8221; or &#8220;Say something nice to a cashier&#8221;. You start with &#8220;Self&#8221; missions and move to &#8220;Family&#8221; missions and so on.</p>
<div><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-76055" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/menu_animals_300-169x300.jpg" alt="" width="169" height="300" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/menu_animals_300-169x300.jpg 169w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/menu_animals_300-125x223.jpg 125w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/menu_animals_300.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-76057" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/missions_inner_300-169x300.jpg" alt="" width="169" height="300" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/missions_inner_300-169x300.jpg 169w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/missions_inner_300-125x223.jpg 125w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/missions_inner_300.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-76059" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mission_me_ss03-169x300.png" alt="" width="169" height="300" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mission_me_ss03-169x300.png 169w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mission_me_ss03-768x1366.png 768w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mission_me_ss03-576x1024.png 576w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mission_me_ss03-700x1245.png 700w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mission_me_ss03-125x222.png 125w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mission_me_ss03.png 813w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /></div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<p>This game is engaging and helps you with your own self-esteem. The game is available as a free app on <a href=https://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewSoftware?id=1290528489&mt=8 target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple&#8217;s App Store</a> and <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sillysoft.MissionMe target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a>. Check it out! If you want you can leave feedback to the developer in our <a href=https://forums.coronalabs.com/topic/74139-mission-me-a-real-life-adventure-game-now-available/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">Community Forums</a>!</p>
<p><a href=https://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewSoftware?id=1290528489&mt=8 target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-58814" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/apple2-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a> <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sillysoft.MissionMe target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-72174" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge-150x150.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge-150x150.png 150w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge.png 200w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
