		<item>
		<title>Featured #MadeWithCorona Game: OverRapid</title>
		<link>/blog/2018/06/20/featured-madewithcorona-game-overrapid/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 20 Jun 2018 19:26:34 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Rob Miracle]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Featured App]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">/?p=75831</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Some really amazing games can be #madewithcorona. Check out the music-based rhythm action game OverRapid.]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Corona can be used to make many different kinds of apps, but undoubtedly it&#8217;s a great tool for games. There of course are many different types of games too. We would like to introduce you to <em><a href=https://twitter.com/overrapid target="_blank" rel="noopener">OverRapid</a></em>, a musical puzzle game.</p>
<div class="video-responsive"><iframe width="auto" height="auto" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wEsoyx9cHzw?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
<p><em>OverRapid</em>, created by Byeong-Su Kang of <a href=https://twitter.com/team_arcstar target="_blank" rel="noopener">Team ArcStar</a>, is a mobile rhythm action game similar in style to famous titles like Rock Band and Guitar Hero. <em>OverRapid</em> lets you select songs and you&#8217;re sent notes down rows and tap on the various lines to have the note counted in your score. You have notes you have to just touch to count and other notes you have to &#8220;scratch&#8221; to have counted.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-75832" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/overrapid_ss-1024x576.png" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/overrapid_ss-1024x576.png 1024w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/overrapid_ss-300x169.png 300w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/overrapid_ss-768x432.png 768w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/overrapid_ss-700x394.png 700w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/overrapid_ss-539x303.png 539w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/overrapid_ss-125x70.png 125w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />The game has over 250,000 installs on Google Play and over 116,000 installs on iOS. It also made the Google Indie Game Festival Top 20 in Korea. The game is available as a free download on both <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.arcstar.overrapid target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a> and the <a href=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/overrapid/id994425296?mt=8 target="_blank" rel="noopener">App Store</a> with in-app purchases.</p>
<p><a href=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/overrapid/id994425296?mt=8 target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-72086" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a> <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.arcstar.overrapid target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-67966" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/badge-google-play.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/badge-google-play.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/badge-google-play-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
			</item>
		<item>
		<title>Featured game: Beasts Battle 2</title>
		<link>/blog/2018/02/15/featured-game-beasts-battle-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2018 17:20:18 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Rob Miracle]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Featured App]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">/?p=73309</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Beasts Battle 2 is a game for Windows desktop. Learn more about this #madewithcorona game.]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><em><a href=http://beastsbattle.com/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">Beasts Battle 2</a></em> is the follow up to <em>Beasts Battle</em> from Greenolor Studio, primarily by Sergey Pomorin in Kaliningrad, Russia. Inspired by classics like <em>Heroes of Might and Magic</em> and the <em>King&#8217;s Bounty</em> series, <em>Beasts Battle 2</em> is a turn-based strategy game that operates in one of two game modes: map mode where the player explores the world and battlegrounds mode in which each battle occurs.</p>
<div class="video-responsive"><iframe width="auto" height="auto" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jjRS_BSvzkM?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
<p>During game play you will visit 10 original locations with colorful and diverse battlefields where you will encounter over 40 enemies that will challenge you with special abilities. You will collect unique artifacts, spells and build up your player&#8217;s skills while completing the main quests and additional side quests as you explore the world.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-73314" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_3-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_3-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_3-300x169.jpg 300w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_3-768x432.jpg 768w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_3-700x394.jpg 700w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_3-539x303.jpg 539w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_3-125x70.jpg 125w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><br />
<img src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_4-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-73315" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_4-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_4-300x169.jpg 300w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_4-768x432.jpg 768w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_4-700x394.jpg 700w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_4-539x303.jpg 539w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bb2_1920x1080_4-125x70.jpg 125w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p><em><a href=http://beastsbattle.com/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">Beasts Battle 2</a></em> is available for Windows desktop <a href=http://store.steampowered.com/app/632020/Beasts_Battle_2/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">through Steam</a> for $9.99.</p>
<p><a href=http://store.steampowered.com/app/632020/Beasts_Battle_2/ target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-67654" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/share_steam_logo-300x300.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/share_steam_logo-300x300.png 300w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/share_steam_logo-150x150.png 150w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/share_steam_logo-500x512.png 500w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/share_steam_logo.png 512w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></content:encoded>
