		<item>
		<title>Featured game: The Guides Axiom</title>
		<link>/blog/2018/02/07/featured-game-the-guides-axiom/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2018 20:04:42 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Rob Miracle]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Featured App]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">/?p=73297</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<em>The Guides Axiom</em> is a follow up hit to <em>The Guides</em>. Learn more about this fantastic #madewithcorona game.]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In 2015, Kansas City developer Kevin Bradford and art director Luke Lisi put out a beautiful puzzle game <em><a href=https://theguidesapp.com/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Guides</a></em>. <em>The Guides</em> received high accolades from many including Apple&#8217;s &#8220;<em>15 Most Mind-Bending Puzzlers</em>&#8221; and CNET&#8217;s &#8220;<em>Best Mobile Games of 2015</em>&#8220;.</p>
<p>The team has followed this hit up with a sequel <em><a href=https://theguidesapp.com/axiom/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Guides Axiom</a></em>.</p>
<p>It has over a million downloads and has been featured in Apple&#8217;s <em>&#8220;New Games We Love&#8221;</em> category and Google Play&#8217;s <em>&#8220;New Indie Highlights&#8221;</em> category just after its release in September, 2017.</p>
<div class="video-responsive"><iframe width="auto" height="auto" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3WyD96Zq8Cw?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
<p>It&#8217;s a beautiful, well-crafted game that provides the player various puzzles to solve and ciphers to decode, presented in unique and challenging ways. The game contains over 50 meticulously-designed challenges with more on the way. It also features nonlinear game play allowing you to explore the game at your pace and interest.</p>
<div><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-73298" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom1-169x300.jpg" alt="" width="169" height="300" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom1-169x300.jpg 169w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom1-577x1024.jpg 577w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom1-125x222.jpg 125w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom1.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-73299" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom2-169x300.gif" alt="" width="169" height="300" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom2-169x300.gif 169w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom2-125x222.gif 125w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-73300" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom3-169x300.png" alt="" width="169" height="300" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom3-169x300.png 169w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom3-577x1024.png 577w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom3-125x222.png 125w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/axiom3.png 640w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /></div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<p>Luke and Kevin hate &#8220;pay to win&#8221; games, so they have set up a unique support system based on how much you like or love the game as well as being able to buy &#8220;hacks&#8221; to help when you get stuck. The Guides Axiom is available on <a href=https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1265157039 target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple&#8217;s App Store</a>, <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kevinbradford.games.axiom target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a> and <a href=https://www.amazon.com/gp/mas/dl/android?p=com.kevinbradford.games.axiom target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazon</a> as a free download.</p>
<p><a href=https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1265157039 target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-72086" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a> <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kevinbradford.games.axiom target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-72174" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a> <a href=https://www.amazon.com/gp/mas/dl/android?p=com.kevinbradford.games.axiom target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-72087" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/amazon-icon-badge-large-200.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/amazon-icon-badge-large-200.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/amazon-icon-badge-large-200-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
			</item>
		<item>
		<title>Featured Game: Zombie Guard</title>
		<link>/blog/2018/01/04/featured-game-zombie-guard/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2018 23:09:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Rob Miracle]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Featured App]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">/?p=73255</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[The game Zombie Guard has been a great success for its developer. Read on to learn more about this #madewithcorona game.]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Elliot Pace at <a href=http://www.epacegames.com/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epace Games LLC</a> can put a feather in his cap. His game <em>Zombie Guard</em> has broken the one million download mark, a dream for almost every app developer. The game also earned the Google Play Editor&#8217;s Choice selection!</p>
<div class="video-responsive"><iframe width="auto" height="auto" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GaY7-Yp6G8k?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
<p>In <em>Zombie Guard</em>, you defend your city from an onslaught of zombies. You pick up weapons, power ups and other equipment to boost your abilities. You can also get other allies to help and gain even more loot.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-73256" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/zombie_guard_ss.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="540" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/zombie_guard_ss.jpg 960w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/zombie_guard_ss-300x169.jpg 300w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/zombie_guard_ss-768x432.jpg 768w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/zombie_guard_ss-700x394.jpg 700w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/zombie_guard_ss-539x303.jpg 539w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/zombie_guard_ss-125x70.jpg 125w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
<p>According to Pace, this is by far his most successful game. Between ads and in-app purchases, he&#8217;s able to travel the world as a digital nomad. <em>Zombie Guard</em> is free and available from both <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.epacegames.zombiemobile&hl=en target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a> and <a href=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id1106182796 target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple&#8217;s App Store</a>.</p>
<p><a href=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id1106182796 target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-72086" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a> <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.epacegames.zombiemobile&hl=en target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-72174" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
