		<item>
		<title>Featured Game: Triogical</title>
		<link>/blog/2017/12/28/featured-game-triogical/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2017 21:45:42 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Rob Miracle]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Featured App]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">/?p=73234</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Triogical is a puzzle game that is based on three wizards with different powers. Learn more about this #madewithcorona game]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href=http://www.triogical.com/us/ target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Triogical</em></a> is a puzzle game from <a href=http://www.jealogic.com/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jealogic</a>, a two person studio located in France. The game is based on three wizards with different powers that can collect gems, move objects and destroy objects. You move from puzzle to puzzle solving each one using a combination of the wizards powers.</p>
<div class="video-responsive"><iframe width="auto" height="auto" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XlzvTSuBH98?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
<p>The game features several castles to explore, with about fifty levels each. Your goals is to try and clear each level in as few moves as possible to collect the most stars. Earn enough stars to unlock other castle islands. Each castle has even tougher objects and more ingenious puzzles to solve.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-73235" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ss01-1024x607.png" alt="" width="1024" height="607" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ss01-1024x607.png 1024w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ss01-300x178.png 300w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ss01-768x455.png 768w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ss01-700x415.png 700w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ss01-125x74.png 125w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ss01.png 1518w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p><a href=http://www.triogical.com/us/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">Triogical</a> is available on <a href=https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1256327081 target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple&#8217;s App Store</a> and <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jealogic.triogicalB2 target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a> for free and contains in-app purchases.</p>
<p><a href=https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1256327081 target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-72086" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a>   <a href=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jealogic.triogicalB2 target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-72174" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/google-play-badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
