		<item>
		<title>Featured Game: COLOR FENCE</title>
		<link>/blog/2017/11/21/featured-game-color-fence/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2017 16:17:53 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Rob Miracle]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Featured App]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">/?p=72990</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Check out COLOR FENCE from McPeppergames which was featured by Apple in the App Store!]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The crack team at <a href=http://www.mcpeppergames.com/ target="_blank" rel="noopener">McPeppergames UG (haftungsbeschraenkt) &amp; Co. KG</a> has scored big with their game <a href=http://www.mcpeppergames.com/blog/?p=222 target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>COLOR FENCE</em></a>. It got featured by Apple on the front page of the App Store in the &#8220;<strong>New Games We Love!</strong>&#8221; category. McPeppergames was founded in 2013 by educator Daniela Mach and mobile game veteran Chris Noeth with a focus on high quality kids apps, but they also produce games for everyone.</p>
<div class="video-responsive"><iframe width="auto" height="auto" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DefwghXOges?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
<p><em>COLOR FENCE</em> is a game where your job is to wall off blocks of a set of colors while excluding other colored blocks. The game starts simple and ramps up in complexity and challenge quickly. The game includes multiple themes and has surprise modes as you move through the game.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-72991" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/392x696bb-1024x606.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="606" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/392x696bb-1024x606.jpg 1024w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/392x696bb-300x178.jpg 300w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/392x696bb-768x455.jpg 768w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/392x696bb-700x414.jpg 700w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/392x696bb-125x74.jpg 125w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/392x696bb.jpg 1176w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p><em>COLOR FENCE</em> is available from the <a href=https://itunes.apple.com/app/color-fence/id1263833188?mt=8 target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple App Store</a> for free with in-app purchases.</p>
<p><a href=https://itunes.apple.com/app/color-fence/id1263833188?mt=8 target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-72086" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge.png 200w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/App-Store-Icon_200x200_badge-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px" /></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
